@startuml seq_recovery
title Ghost session -> LOST -> re-queue -> re-place (recovery, #13)
skinparam shadowing false
participant Control
participant Scheduler
database Store
participant "Provider A\n(colab, flaky)" as A
participant "Provider B\n(slurm)" as B

Control -> A : place(Job, Slot_A)
A --> Control : Placement_A (RUNNING)
Control -> Store : Job -> RUNNING

... rapid session churn ...

Control -> A : poll(Placement_A)
A --> Control : LOST (session dropped)
note over Control, Store
  reconcile: RUNNING -> QUEUED,
  attempts++, release Slot_A capacity.
  A misbehaving poll that RAISES is
  caught at the seam -> DEGRADED, tick still completes.
end note
Control -> Store : Job -> QUEUED

== next tick(now) ==
Control -> B : offer(requirements)
B --> Control : [ Slot_B (queued, wait 5m) ]
Control -> Scheduler : tick(...)
Scheduler --> Control : deadline slack ok -> place Job -> Slot_B
Control -> Store : reserve() atomic (Job -> PLACING)
Control -> B : place(Job, Slot_B)
B --> Control : Placement_B (RUNNING)
note over Control : invariant: a non-cancelled job\nis never silently lost
@enduml
